				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2020 03:26:11 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Hydrails-EPSILON</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5348862</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Well&#8230;. Lee Hsien Loong <strong>is</strong> the Prime Minister of Singapore. You wanted to avoid using the real Prime Minister but ended up doing so anyway.</p> <p>Might want to quickly change.</p> <p>Also, in your email to the poet, be honest with everything: that the SCP is not exactly complimentary of Singapore (the opposite, actually), that it casts a treasured monument of Singapore in a rather darker light, all that&#8230;</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
