				<wikidot:authorName>caspian2</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5343993</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div style="text-align: center;"> <p><em>You rose by the Bay,</em><br /> <em>bayed by the unknown,</em><br /> <em>glistening guardian of</em><br /> <em>murky waters pooled</em><br /> <em>through hearts of white,</em><br /> <em>your insides choked by</em><br /> <em>reality, then regurgitated</em><br /> <em>off porcelain lips.</em></p> </div> <br /> <div style="text-align: right;"> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">poetry&nbsp;credits:</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">the&nbsp;horrible&nbsp;poetry</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>belongs to me.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> <p>My fourth scip. Know it may not be everyone’s cup of tea, but hey, I had fun writing it :)</p> <p>My sincere thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scottyhoff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5855939&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591963837" alt="Scottyhoff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5855939)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scottyhoff" >Scottyhoff</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5336470&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591963837" alt="cybersqyd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5336470)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cybersqyd" >cybersqyd</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/haydenhead" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3057100&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591963837" alt="Haydenhead" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3057100)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/haydenhead" >Haydenhead</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/marcelles-raynes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5722579&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591963837" alt="Marcelles_Raynes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5722579)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/marcelles-raynes" >Marcelles_Raynes</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/percevale" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5980842&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591963837" alt="Percevale" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5980842)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/percevale" >Percevale</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sonderance" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6091992&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1591963837" alt="Sonderance" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6091992)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sonderance" >Sonderance</a></span> for helping me polish it up.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;Image&nbsp;Sources</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">⊟&nbsp;Sources</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <ul> <li>First image: <a href="https://www.piqsels.com/el/public-domain-photo-jsxpu/">https://www.piqsels.com/el/public-domain-photo-jsxpu/</a> (CC0)</li> <li>Second Image: <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Lee_Hsien_Loong,_Institute_for_Strategic_Studies_conference,_2007.JPG">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Lee_Hsien_Loong,_Institute_for_Strategic_Studies_conference,_2007.JPG</a> (CC0)</li> <li>Third image: <a href="https://www.publicdomainpictures.net/en/view-image.php?image=51195&amp;picture=merlion-park-singapore">https://www.publicdomainpictures.net/en/view-image.php?image=51195&amp;picture=merlion-park-singapore</a> (CC0)</li> <li>Fourth image: <a href="https://www.wallpaperflare.com/singapore-aerial-hdb-flats-houses-road-clouds-sky-drone-wallpaper-eazlk">https://www.wallpaperflare.com/singapore-aerial-hdb-flats-houses-road-clouds-sky-drone-wallpaper-eazlk</a> (CC0)</li> <li>Parts of Addendum xxxx-02 adapted from: <a href="https://www.pmo.gov.sg/Newsroom/speech-mr-lee-hsien-loong-prime-minister-singapore-human-capital-summit-opening-29">https://www.pmo.gov.sg/Newsroom/speech-mr-lee-hsien-loong-prime-minister-singapore-human-capital-summit-opening-29</a></li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> <p>Thanks for reading!</p> 
